酷友有要的，去给我暗号（酷友），给大家便宜[微笑]&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/6320887e729600a98ca821b66df5795a.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/dfd4ddd06e2b9e5e938a9b4749de6163.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/e7f571a862df576f098a343e76137f0c.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/6695afce830aca6705115f64257580d5.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/c5b9e426be6c55f328cbecd04232d533.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/266fa27ffbcc459b1a28736ed003056d.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/392dec4c6222794c2fce7172173cead4.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/e406a1ca86ff4a25e2305c81f5957505.jpg&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/a84624caf590d5f46dc5c43108897a61.jpg&quot; &gt;</description><link>https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70935327</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.coolapk.com/feed/70935327</guid><pubDate>Sat, 28 Mar 2026 12:54:52 GMT</pubDate><author>App大师</author></item><item><title>望远镜支架做成这个样子，等 3D 打印机热床打印板到了就打印出来，底下用 M5 的热熔螺母可以安装在三角支架上面用 #3D打印# 话说皇冠CAD对于我这种建模少的solid...</title><description>&lt;p&gt;望远镜支架做成这个样子，等 3D 打印机热床打印板到了就打印出来，底下用 M5 的热熔螺母可以安装在三角支架上面用 &lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/3D%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0?type=0&quot;&gt;#3D打印#&lt;/a&gt; 话说皇冠CAD对于我这种建模少的solidworks盗版用户来说，反而更好用，还不用本地安装&lt;a class=&quot;feed-link-tag&quot; href=&quot;https://www.coolapk.com/t/DIY?type=0&quot;&gt;#DIY#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/8363acdd3dcd59e54647a6cb5da25bb9.png&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/79a1c20b7802eb35bbe1f94a8ac72eed.png&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0ce27acf3acdb437a5a2397468d05b89.png&quot; &gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://10.0.0.1:50108/coolapk_img/0ee54caaa66290b5fcc09e4804270